# Tests that a graph can be created, a pair of nodes and
# an edge between them can be added, and a pair of nodes
# and a single edge can be printed out.

# Create a graph
CreateGraph TheLordOfTheRing1

# Add a pair of nodes
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing1 Bilbo
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing1 Gandalf

# Add an edge
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing1 Bilbo Gandalf TheHobbit

# Print the nodes in the graph and the outgoing edges from Bilbo
ListNodes TheLordOfTheRing1
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing1 Bilbo